<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Flag_of_Germany&action=edit&section=8.php.html" title="Edit section: Flag days">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Flag_days">Flag days</span></h2>
<p>Following federal <a href="Decree" title="Decree">decree</a> on 22 March 2005, the flag must be flown from public buildings on the following dates. Not all of these days are public holidays.</p>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:MuensterStadtweinhaus.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/91/MuensterStadtweinhaus.jpg/220px-MuensterStadtweinhaus.jpg" width="220" height="293" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/91/MuensterStadtweinhaus.jpg/330px-MuensterStadtweinhaus.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/91/MuensterStadtweinhaus.jpg/440px-MuensterStadtweinhaus.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:MuensterStadtweinhaus.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf8/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
The <span lang="de" xml:lang="de"><i>Stadtweinhaus</i></span> in <a href="M%C3%BCnster" title="Münster">Münster</a> with banners displayed in mourning (note the black ribbons atop each mast) after the death of former German president <a href="Johannes_Rau" title="Johannes Rau">Johannes Rau</a> in 2006</div>
</div>
</div>
